$ Microsoft Exchange

{ Determine Version of Exchange Server with Outlook #determine-exchange-version

  The steps to find out which version of Exchange → Microsoft/Office/Outlook is connecting to are:
    • Right-click the tray icon of Outlook while holding the *Ctrl* key pressed
    • In the popup menu, choose *Connection Status…*
    • The version is then displayed in the far-right column *Version*

}
